item.title: CV
item.author: me@example.com (sharadcodes)
item.description: Alex Hollomby Profile Versatile individual looking to begin a career in data analytics. Thorough understanding of the data analysis process and strong technical proficiency in a variety of tools used for analysis, including Excel, R, SQL, and Tableau. Experienced in understanding stakeholder requirements, processing and cleaning data, creating visualisations and presenting findings. Recognised as able to work effectively both independently and as part of team. Having completed the Google Data Analytics Certificate, carried out a case study that can be viewed on my personal portfolio at alexdata1.
